<https://w3id.org/dpp/alignment/dpp-dppo/DPP_DPPO_0003> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Semantically equivalent: both capture the matter constituting products/parts. Subclass mapping (dppo:Material ⊑ dppo:Product) reflects DPPO’s flexibility; DPP’s modular placement preserves structure. Alignment preserves CE relevance (resource loops, recyclability)." .
